sequenceDiagram
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService<br/>payload processor
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Serving
    participant CloudEvt as Kubeflow CloudEvent<br/>Broker
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>(PVC/MinIO/DB)
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant KModel as KServe Model<br/>Endpoint

    rect rgb(235, 245, 255)
        Note over KServe,Storage: Flow 1: Model Inference Data Ingestion (KServe v2)
        KServe->>TrustyAI: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP, No encryption
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: PayloadStorage<br/>(buffer partial payloads)
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: PayloadReconciler<br/>(match input+output by ID)
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Persist complete Dataframe<br/>(CSV to PVC /inputs, or S3, or JDBC)
    end

    rect rgb(235, 255, 235)
        Note over ModelMesh,Storage: Flow 1b: ModelMesh Variant
        ModelMesh->>TrustyAI: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>Protobuf-encoded partials<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Reconcile partials
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Persist Dataframe
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 235)
        Note over CloudEvt,Storage: Flow 4: Kubeflow CloudEvent Ingestion
        CloudEvt->>TrustyAI: CloudEvent (Funqy trigger)<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: CloudEventConsumer<br/>→ KServeInferencePayloadReconciler
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Persist Dataframe
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 255)
        Note over Prom,Storage: Flow 2: Scheduled Metrics Computation
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: PrometheusScheduler<br/>(cron trigger, default 5s)
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Read Dataframe
        Storage-->>TrustyAI: Inference data
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Compute SPD, DIR, drift metrics<br/>Update Micrometer gauges<br/>(trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir)
        Prom->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        TrustyAI-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(trustyai_* gauges)
    end

    rect rgb(235, 235, 255)
        Note over User,KModel: Flow 3: On-Demand Explanation
        User->>TrustyAI: POST /explainers/local/lime<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>TLS optional (4443/TCP)<br/>Auth: proxy-delegated
        TrustyAI->>KModel: Inference calls (perturbations)<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP or HTTP<br/>Encryption varies
        KModel-->>TrustyAI: Prediction results
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Compute LIME explanation
        TrustyAI-->>User: JSON explanation response<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Note over User,TrustyAI: Flow 3b: On-Demand Fairness/Drift Metric
        User->>TrustyAI: POST /metrics/group/fairness/spd<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Read Dataframe
        Storage-->>TrustyAI: Inference data
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Compute SPD metric
        TrustyAI-->>User: JSON metric result
    end
